  "texts": [
    "As this field continues to evolve, a collaborative and multidisciplinary approach will be paramount in harnessing the full potential of these technologies, ensuring a secure, efficient, and scalable IoT ecosystem [176,177].",
    "Security challenge of testing datasetsTesting and training are essential for ML/DL applications, and secure and trusted datasets are needed.",
    "Providing such datasets is a significant challenge for IoT applications and can be studied as future work in this regard.",
    "Integration of ML/DL with metaheuristic algorithmsMetaheuristic algorithms can integrate ML/DL and IoT security.",
    "These new algorithms can improve the parameter selection and tuning operations in the security of IoT devices and applications."
